## Modifications

The original RisingWave configurations have been modified to include:
- NATS JetStream integration for message streaming
- Kafka (Redpanda) sinks for downstream processing
- CloudEvents-based data generation and processing
- Enhanced monitoring with custom Grafana dashboards
- Makefile-based automation for pipeline management
- Comprehensive documentation and examples

These modifications are provided under the MIT License.
